platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Control Mario with just a tap!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: He's here! We're all about pulling off stylish moves with a single tap, thanks to super-simple, one-touch controls. But collecting all the pink coins? That takes skill. With tons of unlocks (including Luigi!), youll be playing this one long after you reach the final flagpole.
